{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "d66e6872-da12-4c8d-a8b0-d7ab8caab54e", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d66e6872-da12-4c8d-a8b0-d7ab8caab54e@3.pkg/1772597600744/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597601623", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d66e6872-da12-4c8d-a8b0-d7ab8caab54e@3.pkg/1772597600744/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597601623"}, "identifier": "d66e6872-da12-4c8d-a8b0-d7ab8caab54e", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>依据教材知识,2020年我国全面建成小康社会实现第一个百年奋斗目标；从2020年到2035年,在全面建成小康社会的基础上,再奋斗十五年,基本实现社会主义现代化；从2035年到本世纪中叶,在基本实现现代化的基础上，再奋斗十五年,把我国建成富强民主文明和谐美丽的社会主义现代化强国。所以2024年15岁的李彤到43岁时是2052年,和全国人民共同见证我国全面建成社会主义现代化强国,是有可能实现的,D正确；A错误,全面小康的目标已经实现；B错误,李彤22岁是2031年,2035年我国才基本实现现代化；C错误,李彤30岁是2039年,我国尚未实现中国梦。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>2024年是五四运动爆发105周年。习近平总书记寄语新时代青年：要继承和发扬五四精神,在推进强国建设、民族复兴伟业中展现青春作为、彰显青春风采、贡献青春力量。对此,15岁的中学生李彤开始畅想自己未来的人生轨迹,其中有可能实现的是（ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "2024年是五四运动爆发105周年。习近平总书记寄语新时代青年：要继承和发扬五四精神,在推进强国建设、民族复兴伟业中展现青春作为、彰显青春风采、贡献青春力量。对此,15岁的中学生李彤开始畅想自己未来的人生轨迹,其中有可能实现的是（    ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d66e6872-da12-4c8d-a8b0-d7ab8caab54e@3.pkg/item.json?v=1754839815735", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>20岁,在大学举办“加快实现全面小康”班会活动</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>22岁,出去旅游一趟,感受我国基本实现现代化的变化</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>30岁,和好友相约一起去北京天安门共祝祖国实现中国梦</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>43岁,和全国人民共同见证我国全面建成社会主义现代化强国</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>2024年是五四运动爆发105周年。习近平总书记寄语新时代青年：要继承和发扬五四精神,在推进强国建设、民族复兴伟业中展现青春作为、彰显青春风采、贡献青春力量。对此,15岁的中学生李彤开始畅想自己未来的人生轨迹,其中有可能实现的是（ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "$RE0200", "5036342748", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "d66e6872-da12-4c8d-a8b0-d7ab8caab54e", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "2024年是五四运动爆发105周年。习近平总书记寄语新时代青年：要继承和发扬五四精神,在推进强国建设、民族复兴伟业中展现青春作为、彰显青春风采、贡